            <title>[LU-2805] Test failure on test suite sanity, subtest test_184c</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2805</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Nathaniel Clark &amp;lt;nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b5d3877a-7548-11e2-93d9-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b5d3877a-7548-11e2-93d9-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_184c failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Content mismatch [0, 42008576) of ref2 and file1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 184c&lt;/p&gt;</description>
